{"tid":768643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 濾水廠兇案死者身有多處致命刀傷 料涉工作糾紛","createTime":"2018-08-05T14:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T03:26:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1ca428ac1bc514d0e0f481d9e11ce585e92de7","tid":768643,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b670723e60383fb6b32b6d2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b670723e60383fb6b32b6d2%2F&d=dgh%2BcIwXMOALXFQC76gWspWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=42958c81\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b670723e60383fb6b32b6d2/</a>"},{"pid":"8b4af026551010e65f683f6dc09373d4e298effd","tid":768643,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"沙田濾水廠發生謀殺案，一名男子死亡，警方拘捕一人。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯被帶返田心警署。警方晚上約六時半接獲一名男子報案，據了解，對方報稱殺死一名同事，他們都是濾水廠保安員。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場在濾水廠保安亭內，發現一名男子倒臥地上，證實死亡，現場有一把菜刀。警方拘捕報案男子。"},{"pid":"4bab74442eb7d45a000982f26523f8e488de349d","tid":768643,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沙田濾水廠旁謀殺案　警方相信動機與工作瑣碎糾紛有關</span><br />\n<br />\n沙田濾水廠對開發生謀殺案，一名58歲男子懷疑被斬死，警方拘捕死者的59歲男同事。<br />\n<br />\n沙田警區助理指揮官陳昕說，傍晚約6時分別接到2個報案，指現場有人被斬傷，警員和救護員到場後，發現男死者倒臥地上，後頸有2至3處致命傷痕，他形容傷口深至見骨，死者流了很多血，到傍晚6點半證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n陳昕相信，疑犯用平時斬樹枝和柴的1.5尺刀行兇，他的衫褲鞋有大量血跡。他又說，死者是工作了5天的替工，與疑犯互不相識，初步掌握疑犯的犯案動機，是<span style=\"color: red;\">工作上瑣碎糾紛引起</span>，目前以謀殺罪拘捕疑犯，將會通宵扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410751-20180805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410751-20180805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dgh%2BcIwXMOALXFQC76gWspWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9f49e19a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410751-20180805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5dc24787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410751-20180805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"551e0beaf8b83d1ca992cb6d07fd1d6a7e7754ea","tid":768643,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多 你辭職未"},{"pid":"3e474bf510c21944da66b78d3b4ae4fe1148b87c","tid":768643,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"22bd9efff581dc505e283a51c7b8b0a93cdb6c83","tid":768643,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"9成係條廢老想屈個替更日日返啲豬頭骨位或者叫佢打曬啲checkpoint,個替更俾人撚左幾日今日唔射佢屌佢老母，點知就俾條廢老斬撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}